Package net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.generator

Interface Summary
ConfigurationAwareResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all resource generator, which wanted to have information about the .
CssResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all objects, which generates CSS resources.
InitializingResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all resource generator, which are aware of property initialization.
LocaleAwareResourceGenerator The interface of objects which can handle locale aware resources
PostInitializationAwareResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all resource generator, which wanted to be triggered when all their properties has been set.
PrefixedResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all resource generators.
ResourceGenerator A ResourceGenerator is acomponent that generates script or CSS dynamically, instead of reading it from the contents of a WAR file.
SpecificCDNDebugPathResourceGenerator The interface for ResourceGenerator which specify the debug path for the CDN.
StreamResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all class which generates image resources.
TypeAwareResourceGenerator This interface is implemented by all resource generator, which wants to be informed of the resource type which they are managing.

GeneratorContext Encapsulates the parameters needed in Generators.
GeneratorRegistry Registry for resource generators, which create scripts or CSS data dynamically, as opposed to the usual behavior of reading a resource from the war file.
IECssBundleGenerator This class defines a generator which will bundle all the CSS defines in parameter.
